Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「命运相连的两人的小指被红线连系在一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以来有着这样的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的红线又与哪里的谁相连在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,practe biginar ardescat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕映夕映真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,practe biginar ardescat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么事可以一朝一夕办成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗马也不是一天建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真想尽快掌握魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最近在图书馆岛探险时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在书架最里面发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…魔法书？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不会就是命运的红线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  这是能知道红线那边是谁的咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想马上学会这个魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样一来  就能知道我命运中的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我们俩都还只是初学者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么难的咒文…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都有擅长和不擅长的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许对我而言比其他人更不费吹灰之力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想知道命运的另一半是谁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据这本书上的记载
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎只要以最真实的感受默念所想的那个人即可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是涅吉老师…希望是涅吉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,practe biginar filum ostrinus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,practe biginar filum ostrinus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是涅吉老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红线延伸向远方…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Negima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不是的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是将命运的红线视觉化的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是将人与人用红线连结起来的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉突然被拽跑了  我还以为发生什么事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为红线所连接…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说来…  我和涅吉老师属于…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这怎么行…好为难…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有做好心理准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别担心  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是晚会上用来调节气氛的小魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上就会消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着那么麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接剪断它怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很碍事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一挂到什么可就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用做到那个程度也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要小心一点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡…卡莫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险啊  差点又有一个新的趣味觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  多危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是剪断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  拜托了  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪不断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  无意中系上的这根红线却意外地结实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕映妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不胜荣幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  不过幸好今天是假日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在红线消失之前  就先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以一直和涅吉老师待在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这儿呀  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家提议一起去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（雪广观光集团）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是雪广观光集团为此最新策划建造的娱乐设施
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻帆良温泉疗养胜地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻帆良温泉疗养胜地？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（近日预定开放  Coming Soon! ）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  作为它的落成纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让涅吉老师最先光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就在正式开业之前  特别对本班开放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请大家尽情地享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉很讨厌洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…这样的我还是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈…  所以很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和涅吉老师一起洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很大规模呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候和涅吉老师发展为手牵手走路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是你想像的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为线太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线…  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和香同学  没有魔力的人似乎是看不见这根红线的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个稀奇的魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可无法赞同这种没有完全掌握就随便使用的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就走了呢  等等啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是危险的魔法的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么认真嘛  不也很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像刑事侦探片一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑事侦探片？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\fs22}嫌疑犯  涅吉{\r}\N涅吉·斯普林菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fs22}警官  和香  (俗称  书店){\r}\N宫琦  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人心跳加速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩也来连连看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那样…  大小姐  请别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:43.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们俩去那边好好休息去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  好好休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  因为这样没办法换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:48.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学你们就别管我们  尽情地享受温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刹～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算就这样来为你讨厌洗澡这件事开脱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  你误会了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别骗人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件破T恤即使撕破了也没什么好可惜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不介意  可和香同学她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没得商量！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉  书店妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师  宫崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  请别在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个傻瓜涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服的温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国哪个州有很多喜欢洗澡的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  因为叫作「入浴」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是纽约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为「洗澡」  所以是佛罗里达～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我如果回答是佛罗里达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是「入浴」  所以是纽约～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人就是这副德行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说气泡温泉可以促进血液循环  加速新陈代谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对皮肤也很有好处  扑露扑露好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气泡温泉还有一个特别先进的功效哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是放屁也不会暴露哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是放屁也不会暴露…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑是也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  这枪可以在水中使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜水汞推进式霰弹捕鱼枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是大白鲨也同样一击必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴池里没有鲨鱼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现这玩意掉在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我正在找它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了  美空？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（要参照Negima春）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又把它带来了吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗得真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又复活了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你要复活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独家新闻独家新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿照相机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会回来  等会再复活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那个意思啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刹  我来帮你擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么可以  大小姐  不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该由我来给大小姐擦背才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那好吧  就拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我办不到  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和涅吉老师一起洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这根红线能够就这样一直连着该有多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裹着浴巾泡澡  是违反礼节的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…在涅吉老师的面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是TV动画！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快把多余的东西拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经洗好了洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下  和香…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  好不容易想凭借色诱事件使两人的关系更进一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈实在是太胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  反正我也洗得快差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去那边喝点果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没好好洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就坐在那儿别动  让我给你好好洗洗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  明日菜同学  我自己能洗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎  明明自己连头发都洗不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了单手还绑着红线呢  这样要怎么洗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的  请别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又打算这样逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来趟这么好的浴池不容易  我一定要给你彻底洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶加濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就料到会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用了两周的时间制造出这台超级便利入浴机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来体验一下触手君MK-V的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标捕捉  清洗开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底为他清洗干净！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞…搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  我指的是涅吉不是我自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜单1  去除衣物开始按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  好痒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来  叶加濑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  取消键不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有2个星期…  这样似乎已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}（麻帆良  日本庭园澡堂）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  Hello  Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有惊人消息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千羽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上现在正在温泉疗养胜地哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲到这里  应该没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极乐极乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来尝试一下超式美容如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美容？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超还会那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有利内分泌腺活性化  美肤效果拔群呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　　　Chiropractic{\r}\N这可是中国式阿修罗按摩与修身脊椎矫正疗法相结合的原创技术哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样  樱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  实在是太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从现在开始才是重头戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give  Give  Give  Give up～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来疲劳就从身体内部烟消云散了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是美容保养
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如说是关节技？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超  那个手臂的姿势不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样  只要2秒就能搞定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…杀了她怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用了厨房做的  水果鸡尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常适合在洗完澡以后饮用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清淡美妙清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有利于补充因出汗而流失的水分和维他命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方干什么呢  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易与老师的关系有了一定的进展
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去可以两人独处的地方可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我知道个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪…哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Banana
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  看招  接着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜者  扎吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  为什么我会输在乒乓球上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎吉真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和杂技技巧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  还有没有其她对战者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确信自己能够战胜扎吉的挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  意外地能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶茶丸  给她点颜色看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Technical Foul{\r}\N技术犯规
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罚退50码
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪个国家的规则啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太习惯这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经  再也无法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不该让小孩洗桑拿浴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  和香同学早上好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气可真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不错  我来摸摸你的头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别跟我客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那我就恭敬不如从命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊  对不起  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到和香同学也有乐天的一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜单25  进行后脑勺的清洗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有3条指令就将结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续努力吧  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 任你处置…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和香是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果她幸福的话我也会感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  对涅吉老师没什么其它的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么这么傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和香  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  夕映同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.43,0:23:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不马上加以制止的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来引导魔力的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请夕映同学也一起用意识来引导
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用意识？  引导？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…重复你在使用魔法时的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你最真实的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用最真实的感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mea virga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最真实的感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和香  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为快死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.48,0:24:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是  怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.82,0:24:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是豆腐渣工程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.77,0:24:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  雪广观光集团是绝对不会出这种差错的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.94,0:24:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.21,0:24:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师  我这里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.25,0:24:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.14,0:24:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.00,0:24:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的红线一定仍然连接着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.53,0:24:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.69,0:24:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一定和某处的某人相连系着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.82,0:24:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.32,0:25:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.91,0:25:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不待在我身边  也不要紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.71,0:25:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.63,0:27:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜单第…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.27,0:27:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就从菜单1重新再来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.73,0:27:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～！
